      "span_text": "A sequence S is called a q-ary modular robust positioning sequence of strength n and distance d, or (n, d) q -MRPS for short, if Next, to construct binary RPS, Berkowitz and Kopparty  used a short binary string called marker and a special mapping to transform symbols from a large alphabet to binary strings."
